{"tid":1386447,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"快啲登記「香港民研意見群組」","createTime":"2019-07-30T10:48:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T17:48:46.000Z","uid":270374,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"86a033a34458b380d542fdd07a5a8e064c7213cb","tid":1386447,"uid":270374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:48:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家快啲登記啦！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.pori.hk/hkpop-panel\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pori.hk%2Fhkpop-panel&d=R3EG5gZ7WKeJnJLyvNLCuZo9Jm%2BrpizTNr1X5Fgg%2Fao%3D&h=283b6590\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.pori.hk/hkpop-panel</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1471376-20190730.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1471376-20190730.htm&d=R3EG5gZ7WKeJnJLyvNLCuZo9Jm%2BrpizTNr1X5Fgg%2Fao%3D&h=5defa33e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1471376-20190730.htm&h=191b3549\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1471376-20190730.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">香港民研已籌得逾500萬元 即日啟動意見群組項目<br />\n</span></strong><br />\n定期就特區官員民望進行民調的港大民意研究計劃，本月起脫離港大轉為獨立機構，改稱「香港民意研究所」，主要透過眾籌支持研究工作。<br />\n<br />\n研究所總監鍾庭耀表示，籌款目標為600萬元，截至今早10時半，網上支付款項籌得506萬元，對發展感到欣慰。他表示，扣除研究所早前撥備48萬元作為首兩個月調查經費，所有籌得款項，包括支票、銀行過戶，及定期捐款等收入，起動基金已有逾500萬元。<br />\n<br />\n鍾庭耀說，研究所今日啟動「香港民研意見組群」項目，發展兩種意見組群，一種為隨機抽樣的「<span style=\"color: red;\">香港市民代表組群</span>」及「<span style=\"color: red;\">香港青年代表組群</span>」，若被抽樣的市民承諾成為成員，將會對其作出定期跟進及訪問。<br />\n<br />\n另一種是自發式「香港市民自結組群」及「香港青年自結組群」，歡迎市民上網登記，<span style=\"color: red;\">登記成員數量達到1萬個，就會開始進行組群式研究工作。</span><br />\n<br />\n鍾庭耀說，<span style=\"color: red;\">計劃啟動後，會向各組群訪問各種實質社會問題，以近日為例，可問組群對港澳辦記招，以及警方就最近遊行發出反對通知書的看法，期望能最快半日內取得市民反應的科學數據，並作出跟進及互動</span>；他又希望日後能進一步設立更多組群，包括銀髮組群、網民組群、少數族裔組群等。"},{"pid":"47ac9bf55ab6075d8b821b6aefea53123d9f93bc","tid":1386447,"uid":78947,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:49:41.000Z","msg":"統計學上算唔算係一種bias?"},{"pid":"974c4843e6ad5d1a799e8fb6861e3ed8b564c2de","tid":1386447,"uid":270374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:51:46.000Z","msg":"都要有個專業機構發聲<br />\n越多連登仔越好"},{"pid":"397f489e23c1e19a9f94982e94541cc6848e2b61","tid":1386447,"uid":52090,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"47ac9bf55ab6075d8b821b6aefea53123d9f93bc","tid":1386447,"uid":78947,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:49:41.000Z","msg":"統計學上算唔算係一種bias?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:52:30.000Z","msg":"我信教授佢會有adjust<br />\n話哂全港統計界最權威一人"},{"pid":"c553b18ea4211b1f0c8d352b5ec69fdc2e68bf27","tid":1386447,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:54:58.000Z","msg":"我驚有bias喎"},{"pid":"cefb1a0238afe5af889f6908136c73482fb0358c","tid":1386447,"uid":78184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:55:45.000Z","msg":"點加入？"},{"pid":"64428811a0e06121459bc27d6753ea1d733aa075","tid":1386447,"uid":4739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T11:17:22.000Z","msg":"點登記"},{"pid":"4a4610dd7beb568fae6dcf461d267814fda81f12","tid":1386447,"uid":4739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c553b18ea4211b1f0c8d352b5ec69fdc2e68bf27","tid":1386447,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:54:58.000Z","msg":"我驚有bias喎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T11:17:40.000Z","msg":"可以講多D嗎"},{"pid":"203d69bcaee68e566a36015999dfb122b0caad8b","tid":1386447,"uid":237175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T11:18:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ad31bcd41303ed086dff657f41c84a7279e2519e","tid":1386447,"uid":129739,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4a4610dd7beb568fae6dcf461d267814fda81f12","tid":1386447,"uid":47